title: Stronger Workout System
description:
The STRONGER Challenge consists of ten 35-minute workouts created by former pro soccer player and celebrity trainer Nicky Holender as well as a FREE daily meal plan created by dietitian Keri Glassman.

There are 10 FREE workout videos and a daily calendar to get you results similar to those promised by popular DVD workout sets that you might pay over $100 for.
 
http://www.livestrong.com/stronger/
